org.openjdk.tools.javac.parser

类 Tokens.Token

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openjdk.tools.javac.parser.Tokens.Token
  • 封闭类:
    Tokens

    public static class Tokens.Token
extends Object
    This is the class representing a javac token. Each token has several fields that are set by the javac lexer (i.e. start/end position, string value, etc).
